description.en: SteamPrices.com is a website that enables anyone to compare prices between regions, such as the US, UK, and many more.
description.ga_IE: Is láithreán gréasáin é Steamprices.com a chuireann ar chumas duine ar bith praghsanna a chur i gcomparáid idir réigiúin, mar shampla na Stáit Aontaithe, an Ríocht Aontaithe, agus go leor eile.
